## Nested Conditional 

<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; padding: 20px;">
        
        <div style="background-color: #F7F8FA; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 8px;">
             <ul>
                <li style = "font-size: 14pt"> Conditional within a conditional</li><br>
                <li style = "font-size: 14pt">Can be nested in the <code>if</code> block or the  <code>else</code> block</li>
             </ul>
        </div>

       
<div>
